Privacy Policy
​
This policy applies to all information collected or submitted on Alpha Studio’s website and any of our apps on any devices and platforms.
Information we collect
If you enable notifications, we must store a token to send them.
We use cookies on the site and similar tokens in the app to keep you logged in. Our server software may also store basic technical information, such as your IP address, in temporary memory or logs.
​
Ads and analytics
The iOS and iPadOS app include third party frameworks such as Google’s AdMobSDK and Facebook’s FacebookSDK. These third parties framework may collect anonymous statistics.
Each of these two frameworks collect certain data as indicated on their websites.
We may deploy AdMob advertising in some/all of our Software and on platforms including mobile devices.
Google is the company running the AdMob service. They may collect user data.
Find here the privacy policy of AdMob:
https://policies.google.com/privacy
You may opt to limit ad tracking on your mobile device, for our mobile apps, by going to the Settings menu and following the appropriate procedure, as defined by the instrucitons of your operating system.
​
Information Usage
We use the information we collect to operate and improve our website and apps.
We may share anonymous, aggregate statistics with outside parties.
​
Information for European Union customers
By using our services and software, you authorize us to collect, use, and store your information inside or outside of the European Union.
​
International Transfer of information
Information may be processed, stored, and used outside of the country in which you are located. Data privacy laws vary across jurisdictions, and different laws may be applicable to your data depending on where it is processed, stored, or used.
​
Your Consent
By using our site or apps, you consent to our privacy policy.